Zahrajeme si na schovávanou, ano?

831
00:59:18,260 --> 00:59:20,140
Tohle je hra na schovávanou.

832
00:59:20,760 --> 00:59:21,900
Vlez tam.

833
00:59:52,230 --> 00:59:54,630
<i>(Hanmiryeo Tteokbokki)</i>

834
00:59:54,630 --> 00:59:56,970
- Dobrý večer.
- To jste vy?

835
00:59:58,270 --> 00:59:59,900
Han Mi Jin někam šla?

836
01:00:00,040 --> 01:00:01,200
Je doma.

837
01:00:02,070 --> 01:00:03,670
Děje se něco?

838
01:00:04,540 --> 01:00:05,640
To nic.

839
01:00:06,610 --> 01:00:07,680
To snad...

840
01:00:09,440 --> 01:00:13,010
